data.description: Welcoming New Listing: Comfort and Convenience in Sable Hills! Welcome to your new charming abode in the heart of the friendly Sable Hills community! This warm and inviting 4-bedroom, 4-bath home perfectly balances everyday comfort with the ease of practical living. Each bedroom, a cozy personal retreat, features its own private bathroom, offering that extra layer of privacy and convenience for family members and guests alike.With over 2,500 square feet of adaptable living space, this residence is designed to support your dynamic lifestyle. The central family room, infused with natural light, serves as the heart of the home, while additional living areas provide the flexibility for a quiet home office, craft room, or play area. The kitchen, functional and bright, is the backdrop for preparing your favorite meals, flanked by a dining space where memories are just waiting to be made. Through the back door, discover not one but two covered seating areas, offering the ideal spot for serene morning coffees or lively weekend BBQs, regardless of the weather.The backyard stands as a testament to simplicity and enjoyment. Revel in the updated pool area, complete with a new liner, efficient equipment, and a solar cover for those not-so-sunny days, reducing maintenance while providing an extended season of splish-splash fun. As dusk falls, gather around the dedicated fire pit area, where storytelling and marshmallow roasting under the starlit sky will become a cherished ritual.Your practical needs are met with the spacious 2-car garage, featuring additional storage space to easily house your tools, seasonal decorations, or recreational gear. Nestled in a community that prides itself on its brand-new pickleball court and convenient boat ramp, this home isn't just a place to live, it's a place to belong. Act now, and take the first step to claim this modest gem as your own. With its combination of thoughtful features and community perks, this ho With its combination of thoughtful features and community perks, this home is anticipated to be a hot topic among buyers. Reach out today, and envision firsthand how this welcoming space fits perfectly into your story. #SableHillsComfort #CommunityGem #YourHomeJourney
